CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 14, 1955, pg. 12 reads: "Teen-Queen And Court - Teen-Queen Barbara Harris and her court composed of runners-up in the contest just ended, sponsored by the Hill City Welfare Department, are shown at the coronation ball held at Ammon Center. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Hill City "Queen" Barbara Harris and her court, gathered on stage in Ammon Center with group of colorguards in foreground, for Coronation Ball
